skins.shipDescription: Iron Blood Type VIIB submarine C U-73.
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm U-73, the Iron Blood submarine that completed lots of missions and served as the leader of several wolfpacks!
skins.acquisition: U-73 of the Iron Blood, reporting for duty! If there's anything that needs doing, just leave it to me!
skins.login: Howdy-do, Commander! Welcome back! I'm all good to go and ready to sortie! Just give me the order.
skins.details: Now, now, Commander, don't stress over everything~ I'm sure it'll all go fine.
skins.secretaryIdle1: When you're underwater all day, sometimes you just wanna resurface and smash through the waves! ... Hey, Commander, wanna go for a quick dive in the ocean?
skins.secretaryIdle2: I'd rather be diving in the ocean and feeling the thrill of being near the enemy than stuck at port staring into space all day...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Isn't it fun to hear what's on somebody's mind and help them with it? ... Maybe I ought to open a psychiatric booth. Anyway, Reichspfennig for your thoughts, Commander?
skins.secretaryTouch: What is it? Got something I could help with? C'mon, tell me something.
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Uh-huh. So, Commander, how many gut-punch torpedoes do you want for dessert?

skins.shipDescription: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!
skins.acquisition: It's time for science class with U-73! Now, Commander, let's try out an exhilarating and positively fascinating experiment!
skins.login: Now we add some of this, thenC Whuah! Don't surprise me like that, Commander! You nearly just caused an accident!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Now we raise the heat slightly, then... Oh, God! I-it's on fire!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Experiments necessitate preciseness. Being even one 100th of a milliliter off affects the result!
skins.secretaryIdle3: The glamor of this lab coat drew me to the science room! ... Huh? This ISN'T a lab coat? Aha, ahahahaha...
skins.secretaryTouch: Hey, Commander? No intimacy right now, okay? I'm fine-tuning this compound, you see...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: You wanna be the target of my experimental fuel-powered torpedoes?
